            <div type="translation">
                <p>Lord, our God, save your people and bless (your inheritance).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In line 4 it seems that the painter modified the incorrect alpha of the first letter of the word λαόν to form the lambda. Text: Second Prayer of the antiphon. 
</p>
